_sText:
My first map, pretty high quality in my opinion Made for a good 5v5 or 10v10, but can handle up to 28 players. Simple indoor slaughter fest. 2 bombsites, a large, cubicle-filled map center, and 2 alternate routes to bombsites/ct spawn. Enjoy! Comes with:
  • Fully juiced map
  • Operational radar and overview
